{"tid":1004100,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TARA朴昭妍曬廣東話冧Fans　想同王祖藍再合作","createTime":"2019-02-01T07:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T17:53:37.000Z","uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ddcb700c7f47781752adff2543ff41b0f818b1fb","tid":1004100,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2383137/org/72a843f470849945c6819c62a6f1aa8c.jpg/bb8dBFiRYXAL6V1V9_im5qLnVdzGMO5XlN7WSJTe1kg?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2383137%2Forg%2F72a843f470849945c6819c62a6f1aa8c.jpg%2Fbb8dBFiRYXAL6V1V9_im5qLnVdzGMO5XlN7WSJTe1kg%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=0827fcf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賀歲片《你咪理，我愛你！》今日（29日）舉行首映禮，有份客串的韓國歌手朴昭妍亦特意飛來香港撐場，近百名粉絲到場支持偶像。昭妍一出場就用廣東話與粉絲打招呼，氹得粉絲尖叫連連。昭妍表示：「好榮幸今次可以參與王祖藍先生的電影拍攝，好開心嚟到香港，亦好開心有咁多粉絲前來支持，又希望大家多多入場支持《你咪理，我愛你！》。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2383133/org/27ce4d075f9ad2c7747e1ee26ab94a7b.jpg/j17uP3aj7bzY2l66gS70zdDowZXp8XMDRkbmo2xG5qM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2383133%2Forg%2F27ce4d075f9ad2c7747e1ee26ab94a7b.jpg%2Fj17uP3aj7bzY2l66gS70zdDowZXp8XMDRkbmo2xG5qM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6173bddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問到拍攝香港電影與韓國的分別，昭妍就說：「這是我第一次參與香港電影的拍攝，與韓國不同的是香港拍攝現場所有事都進行得很快，快之餘也發生了很多趣事，希望下一次不單止是友情演出，而是可以和王祖藍一起合作演戲就好了。」談到2019年的計劃，昭妍的經紀人回應暫時還未定甚麼計劃，粉絲們可能要再等一陣子了。<br />\n<br />\n好殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要R港產片黎拍<br />\nTARA有邊個個景係好D"},{"pid":"af6809f65fbc90d6a588e4b939d67c580241ebcb","tid":1004100,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"成團都係整容+臭閪味八婆<br />\n不過全部都扑野一流"},{"pid":"69c5ebe2b58acb5cba94236892b347c96996f5da","tid":1004100,"uid":177639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"r